{"id":"4a378c65e058","content":"Ryan is joined by  Jeffrey Hightower, VP of Places Data at Microsoft, and Amy Rose, CTO of the Overture Maps Foundation, to chat about their partnership in bringing spatial data to the next generation of Microsoft tools; how Overture’s 50 organization members are creating open, standardized, and interoperable  global spatial data sets; and their solutions to the innate challenges of trying to digitally map the world.​​​​‌﻿‍﻿​‍​‍‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿​‍‌‍‍‌‌‍‌﻿‌‍‍‌‌‍﻿‍​‍​‍​﻿‍‍​‍​‍‌﻿​﻿‌‍​‌‌‍﻿‍‌‍‍‌‌﻿‌​‌﻿‍‌​‍﻿‍‌‍‍‌‌‍﻿﻿​‍​‍​‍﻿​​‍​‍‌‍‍​‌﻿​‍‌‍‌‌‌‍‌‍​‍​‍​﻿‍‍​‍​‍‌‍‍​‌﻿‌​‌﻿‌​‌﻿​​‌﻿​﻿​﻿‍‍​‍﻿﻿​‍﻿﻿‌‍​﻿‌‍﻿‌‌﻿​﻿​‍﻿‍‌﻿​﻿‌﻿‌​‌‍​‌‌‍​﻿‌‍‍﻿‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿‌‍‌‍‌‌‌﻿​‍‌‍‌‍‌‍﻿​‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿‌﻿​‍﻿‍‌‍​﻿‌‍﻿﻿​‍﻿﻿‌‍‍‌‌‍﻿‍‌﻿‌​‌‍‌‌‌‍﻿‍‌﻿‌​​‍﻿﻿‌‍‌‌‌‍‌​‌‍‍‌‌﻿‌​​‍﻿﻿‌‍﻿‌‌‍﻿﻿‌‍‌​‌‍‌‌​﻿﻿‌‌﻿​​‌﻿​‍‌‍‌‌‌﻿​﻿‌‍‌‌‌‍﻿‍‌﻿‌​‌‍​‌‌﻿‌​‌‍‍‌‌‍﻿﻿‌‍﻿‍​﻿‍﻿‌‍‍‌‌‍‌​​﻿﻿‌‌‍‌‌‌‍​﻿‌‍‌‍​﻿‌‍‌‍‌‍​﻿‍​​﻿‍​‌‍‌‍​‍﻿‌​﻿‍​‌‍​﻿​﻿‌​‌‍‌​​‍﻿‌​﻿‌​‌‍​‍‌‍​‌​﻿​‌​‍﻿‌​﻿‍​​﻿‍‌‌‍​‍​﻿​‌​‍﻿‌​﻿​‌​﻿​​​﻿​‍‌‍​‍​﻿‌​​﻿‌‍‌‍​﻿​﻿​‌​﻿‌​‌‍‌​​﻿‍‌​﻿‌‍​﻿‍﻿‌﻿‌​‌﻿‍‌‌﻿​​‌‍‌‌​﻿﻿‌‌‍​‍‌‍﻿​‌‍﻿﻿‌‍‌﻿‌‌​​‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿​﻿‌﻿‌​​﻿‍﻿‌﻿​​‌‍​‌‌﻿‌​‌‍‍​​﻿﻿‌‌‍‌‌‌﻿‍​‌‍​﻿‌‍‌‌‌﻿​‍‌﻿​​‌﻿‌​​﻿﻿﻿‌‍​‍‌‍​‌‌﻿​﻿‌‍‌‌‌‌‌‌‌﻿​‍‌‍﻿​​﻿﻿‌‌‍‍​‌﻿‌​‌﻿‌​‌﻿​​‌﻿​﻿​‍‌‌​﻿​﻿‌​​‌​‍‌‌​﻿​‍‌​‌‍​‍‌‌​﻿​‍‌​‌‍‌‍​﻿‌‍﻿‌‌﻿​﻿​‍﻿‍‌﻿​﻿‌﻿‌​‌‍​‌‌‍​﻿‌‍‍﻿‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿‌‍‌‍‌‌‌﻿​‍‌‍‌‍‌‍﻿​‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿‌﻿​‍﻿‍‌‍​﻿‌‍﻿﻿​‍‌‍‌‍‍‌‌‍‌​​﻿﻿‌‌‍‌‌‌‍​﻿‌‍‌‍​﻿‌‍‌‍‌‍​﻿‍​​﻿‍​‌‍‌‍​‍﻿‌​﻿‍​‌‍​﻿​﻿‌​‌‍‌​​‍﻿‌​﻿‌​‌‍​‍‌‍​‌​﻿​‌​‍﻿‌​﻿‍​​﻿‍‌‌‍​‍​﻿​‌​‍﻿‌​﻿​‌​﻿​​​﻿​‍‌‍​‍​﻿‌​​﻿‌‍‌‍​﻿​﻿​‌​﻿‌​‌‍‌​​﻿‍‌​﻿‌‍​‍‌‍‌﻿‌​‌﻿‍‌‌﻿​​‌‍‌‌​﻿﻿‌‌‍​‍‌‍﻿​‌‍﻿﻿‌‍‌﻿‌‌​​‌‍﻿﻿‌﻿​﻿‌﻿‌​​‍‌‍‌﻿​​‌‍​‌‌﻿‌​‌‍‍​​﻿﻿‌‌‍‌‌‌﻿‍​‌‍​﻿‌‍‌‌‌﻿​‍‌﻿​​‌﻿‌​​‍‌‍‌﻿​​‌‍‌‌‌﻿​‍‌﻿​﻿‌﻿​​‌‍‌‌‌‍​﻿‌﻿‌​‌‍‍‌‌﻿‌‍‌‍‌‌​﻿﻿‌‌﻿​​‌﻿‌‌‌‍​‍‌‍﻿​‌‍‍‌‌﻿​﻿‌‍‍​‌‍‌‌‌‍‌​​‍​‍‌﻿﻿‌"}